shit.”","s":150.16,"e":150.76,"line":51}],"lines":[{"s":3.618,"e":4.333,"text":"Yeah, yeah—"},{"s":4.333,"e":6.909,"text":"Walk in humble, still lit,"},{"s":6.909,"e":10,"text":"I don’t talk too much,"},{"s":10,"e":11.545,"text":"I just hit."},{"s":12.06,"e":14.82,"text":"I’m the shit, no debate, no myth,"},{"s":14.82,"e":18.14,"text":"God gave me gifts, I came with the lift."},{"s":18.24,"e":21.06,"text":"Whole room shift when I step in it,"},{"s":21.06,"e":24.28,"text":"I don’t half-do nothing, I’m built to commit."},{"s":24.2,"e":27.6,"text":"I’m the shit, still blessed, still kind,"},{"s":27.6,"e":30.64,"text":"Sharp in the soul, got fire in the mind."},{"s":31,"e":33.76,"text":"Fell down once, came back legit,"},{"s":33.76,"e":36.9,"text":"Look in the mirror like, “Bro, I’m the shit.”"},{"s":36.9,"e":39.7,"text":"I been through storms, still shine like chrome,"},{"s":39.7,"e":42.9,"text":"Turned cold nights into stepping stones."},{"s":43.18,"e":46,"text":"Had big doubt, had low-day fits,"},{"s":46,"e":49.14,"text":"Now my whole life got highlight clips."},{"s":49.44,"e":51.36,"text":"I don’t need hate, I don’t need clout,"},{"s":51.36,"e":52.98,"text":"I build real things, I figure it out."},{"s":52.98,"e":54.6,"text":"Hands on work, heart on flame,"},{"s":54.6,"e":56.22,"text":"Came from the pain and upgraded the name."},{"s":56.22,"e":58.38,"text":"No half-measures, full-send pressure,"},{"s":58.38,"e":60.38,"text":"Every scar turned into treasure."},{"s":62.16,"e":65.32,"text":"No fake flex, just real grit,"},{"s":65.32,"e":68.8,"text":"Whole soul saying, “I’m the shit.”"},{"s":68.86,"e":71.6,"text":"I’m the shit, no debate, no myth,"},{"s":71.6,"e":74.88,"text":"God gave me gifts, I came with the lift."},{"s":75.06,"e":77.82,"text":"Whole room shift when I step in it,"},{"s":77.82,"e":81.1,"text":"I don’t half-do nothing, I’m built to commit."},{"s":81.02,"e":84.28,"text":"I’m the shit, still blessed, still kind,"},{"s":84.28,"e":87.46,"text":"Sharp in the soul, got fire in the mind."},{"s":87.64,"e":90.5,"text":"Fell down once, came back legit,"},{"s":90.5,"e":93.66,"text":"Look in the mirror like, “Bro, I’m the shit.”"},{"s":93.72,"e":95.68,"text":"Not better than all, just better than fear,"},{"s":95.68,"e":99.06,"text":"I made it this far, so the mission is clear."},{"s":99.72,"e":101.96,"text":"I got bright plans, I got clean intent,"},{"s":101.96,"e":106.12,"text":"I got rent-due hunger with heaven-sent sense."},{"s":106.12,"e":108.14,"text":"They can laugh now, they can switch later,"},{"s":108.14,"e":109.76,"text":"I bless my haters, then I get greater."},{"s":109.76,"e":111.34,"text":"One deep breath, then I lock in quick,"},{"s":111.34,"e":113.42,"text":"Whole world better know I’m the shit."},{"s":113.42,"e":115,"text":"Lit with purpose, lit with grace,"},{"s":115,"e":116.6,"text":"Lit with sunlight on my face."},{"s":116.6,"e":118.14,"text":"Lit through struggle, lit through slips,"},{"s":118.14,"e":123.28,"text":"Lit like truth on holy lips."},{"s":125.78,"e":128.38,"text":"I’m the shit, no debate, no myth,"},{"s":128.38,"e":131.68,"text":"God gave me gifts, I came with the lift."},{"s":131.92,"e":134.64,"text":"Whole room shift when I step in it,"},{"s":134.64,"e":137.76,"text":"I don’t half-do nothing, I’m built to commit."},{"s":138.59,"e":141.04,"text":"I’m the shit, still blessed, still kind,"},{"s":141.04,"e":144.22,"text":"Sharp in the soul, got fire in the mind."},{"s":144.22,"e":147.38,"text":"Fell down once, came back legit,"},{"s":147.38,"e":150.76,"text":"Look in the mirror like, “Bro, I’m the shit.”"}],"duration":195.2,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.307Z","stats":{"whisperWords":388,"polishedWords":390,"matched":354,"matchRate":0.908}}